---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Servicios de Ingeniería de Datos">
  <div class="container mx-auto space-y-16">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-accent/40 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/40 via-primary/60 to-background/90 backdrop-blur-2xl px-8 py-16 md:py-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 animate-fade-in mb-12">
      <div class="flex-1 z-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-5 drop-shadow-xl">
          Descubre el <span class="text-accent">Poder de tus Datos</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl drop-shadow">
          Nuestras soluciones de <span class="text-accent font-semibold">Business Intelligence</span> te ayudan a convertir datos complejos en insights accionables y crecimiento real.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#demo" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-accent/90 text-background font-bold text-lg shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-accent animate-glow">Solicitar Demo</a>
          <a href="#mas" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-accent text-accent font-bold text-lg shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-accent hover:text-background hover:scale-105">Conocer Más</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="bg-white/10 border-2 border-accent rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center animate-fade-in">
          <!-- Icono representativo -->
          <svg width="80" height="80" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="text-accent">
            <rect width="80" height="80" rx="20" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
            <path d="M8 17V10M12 17V7M16 17V13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <style>
        .animate-glow {
          box-shadow: 0 0 24px #00F0FF88, 0 0 8px #6A6AFF44;
          animation: glow-btn 2s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes glow-btn {
          from { box-shadow: 0 0 24px #00F0FF44, 0 0 8px #6A6AFF22; }
          to   { box-shadow: 0 0 48px #00F0FF99, 0 0 24px #6A6AFF66; }
        }
      </style>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-10 text-white text-center drop-shadow-lg">
        Soluciones de <span class="block mt-2 text-accent font-extrabold text-2xl md:text-3xl drop-shadow-glow">Ingeniería de Datos</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Arquitectura de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Diseñamos soluciones de arquitectura de datos flexibles y accesibles que guían el flujo de información en su empresa.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Implementación de Data Lake</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Gestione grandes volúmenes de datos sin procesar, preparándolos para análisis avanzados y mejorando la productividad.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Almacenes de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Creamos repositorios centralizados que recopilan información de múltiples fuentes para análisis empresarial.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 16l4-4m0 0l-4-4m4 4H7m6 4v1a3 3 0 01-3 3H6a3 3 0 01-3-3V7a3 3 0 013-3h4a3 3 0 013 3v1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Migración a Cloud</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Migramos sus datos a la nube de forma rápida, segura y rentable, maximizando la eficiencia empresarial.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Gestión de Datos y Cumplimiento</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Garantizamos la protección y cumplimiento normativo de sus datos, asegurando seguridad y conformidad.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl border-2 border-accent/40 rounded-3xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-500 p-8">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Análisis y Visualización de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Transformamos datos complejos en insights accionables mediante herramientas avanzadas de análisis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/80 via-primary/70 to-background/80 backdrop-blur-2xl border-4 border-accent/30 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 animate-fade-in">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none rounded-3xl" style="box-shadow: 0 8px 64px 0 #00F0FF33, 0 2px 8px 0 #6A6AFF22;"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-white drop-shadow-xl">
      Transformación de Datos <span class="block text-accent md:inline">a Gran Escala</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium drop-shadow">
      Nuestras soluciones de ingeniería de datos están diseñadas para manejar volúmenes masivos de información, proporcionando insights precisos y oportunos.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6 mt-8">
      <a href="#contacto" class="inline-block bg-accent/90 hover:bg-accent text-white font-bold px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl shadow-xl glow-btn text-lg tracking-wide transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent">Solicitar Consulta</a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="inline-block border-2 border-accent text-accent font-bold px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl shadow-xl bg-white/90 hover:bg-accent hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent">Conocer Más</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    <section class="py-16 animate-fade-in bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-accent text-center">
        Beneficios de la <span class="text-accent">Ingeniería de Datos</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Mejora de la Calidad de Datos</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Optimizamos la integridad y precisión de sus datos, eliminando inconsistencias y mejorando su valor.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
          </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Maximización de Macrodatos</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Aprovechamos todo el potencial de sus datos, transformándolos en recursos estratégicos para la toma de decisiones.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Aumento de Productividad</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Automatizamos procesos de datos, liberando recursos para iniciativas estratégicas de mayor valor.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_#00F0FF88] transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in">
          <div class="text-accent mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 stroke-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3-2-1.343-2-3-2zM9 12a3 3 0 100 6 3 3 0 000-6zm6 0a3 3 0 100 6 3 3 0 000-6z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Reducción de Costes</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-center">
            Optimizamos la infraestructura de datos para reducir gastos operativos y mejorar la eficiencia.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 animate-fade-in bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-accent text-center">
        Tecnologías de <span class="text-accent">Ingeniería de Datos</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center animate-fade-in">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 256 296" fill="none">
            <path d="M128 0l-80 48v96l80 48 80-48V48L128 0z" fill="#5382A1"/>
            <path d="M0 128l128 72 128-72v96l-128 72-128-72v-96z" fill="#1B6AC6"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-accent text-center">Java</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt/80 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center animate-fade-in">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="none">
            <path d="M128 0C57.308 0 0 57.308 0 128s57.308 128 128 128 128-57.308 128-128S198.692 0 128 0z" fill="#F0DB4F"/>
